<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Some 'best practice'  recommendations may already be added to Zend_Search_Lucene module documentation.</p>

<ol><li><p>Don't use 'id' for stored field names.</p></li>
<li><p>Some recommendations for MaxBufferedDocs, MaxMergeDocs and MergeFactor settings for different usage modes (indexing, searching, batch indexing, indexing small/large documents).</p></li>
<li><p>Shut down index before the end of script (unset index object), so auto-commit will be done <em>before</em> exception mechanism is shut down.</p></li>
</ol>
    </div>
